Package edu.uky.cs.nil.sabre.hg

Class List<T>

java.lang.Object
edu.uky.cs.nil.sabre.hg.List<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of element in the list
All Implemented Interfaces:
Countable, Serializable, Iterable<T>
public class List<T> extends Object implements Iterable<T>, Serializable, Countable
A list for holding elements of a HeuristicGraph heuristic graph. This list is implemented similarly to an array list, but the method to add to it is package-private to prevent outside modification and the method to remove all elements runs in constant time. These lists are primary used when heuristic graph nodes need to maintain lists of other nodes in the graph.
Author:
Stephen G. Ware
